name: flatstar
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "flatstar" %}
{% set version = "0.2.1a" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/ladsantos/flatstar/archive/refs/tags/v0.2.1-alpha.tar.gz
  sha256: 112ecbedd6f38a8078478b69d36fdc552d7730b61c86d321bbeb452181ce716c

build:
  noarch: python

  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.6
    - pip
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python >=3.6
    - numpy
    - pillow

test:
  imports:
    - flatstar
  commands:
    - pytest
  requires:
    - pytest
  source_files:
    - tests/

about:
  home: https://github.com/ladsantos/flatstar
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'Make 2d intensity maps of limb-darkened stars.'
  doc_url: https://flatstar.readthedocs.io/
  dev_url: https://ladsantos.org

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ladsantos
